{"id":8069,"date":"2021-01-31T21:21:32","date_gmt":"2021-02-01T05:21:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/?page_id=8069"},"modified":"2025-06-21T17:38:41","modified_gmt":"2025-06-22T00:38:41","slug":"chuck-t-murphy-esq","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/chuck-t-murphy-esq\/","title":{"rendered":"Chuck T. Murphy, Esq."},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8858&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<strong>Chuck T. Murphy, Esq.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Lead Trial Counsel<\/p>\n<p>Email: <a href=\"&#109;&#x61;&#x69;&#108;&#x74;&#x6f;:&#x69;&#x6e;f&#111;&#x40;m&#117;&#x72;p&#104;&#x6c;a&#119;&#x2e;n&#101;&#x74;\">&#x69;n&#x66;&#111;&#64;&#x6d;&#117;&#x72;&#112;h&#x6c;&#97;&#x77;&#46;n&#x65;&#116;<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Phone: <a href=\"tel:4152179456\">415-217-9456<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;3\/4&#8243;][vc_column_text]<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Chuck T. Murphy, Esq. is a veteran trial attorney with over 38 years worth of experience. Michael, Sr. has successfully tried over 90 trials during his career consisting of jury trials, bench trials, and arbitration proceedings. He is lead trial counsel at his firm and is at the tip of the spear in tackling every legal issue.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mr. Murphy is an aggressive attorney who seeks effective and efficient resolution for all of his clients. The legal services offered by his firm are unique in that every client is given close personal attention from beginning to end. \u00a0As a result, the relationships formed over the years have endured for decades. Each and every client matters to him and he feels that it is his calling to help people.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael also has an edge over the competition in that he has worked on both the plaintiff and defense side in all various types of lawsuits. Working on both sides of a dispute has allowed him to out-maneuver his opponents. Being able to see multiple angles and points of view in any given case has allowed him to gain a competitive advantage over the opposing lawyers. His experience and the depths of his legal knowledge protects his clients in complex lawsuits.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Although Michael has dedicated his life to serving his clients through his legal services, he has also dedicated countless hours of volunteer work toward helping not only local, but international communities. He believes it is his life mission to give back to those in need and who struggle the most. His law firm has offered free legal services dedicated to the formation and operation of numerous non-profit organizations.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">In 1981,\u00a0Michael\u00a0graduated with his Juris Doctor from Southwestern University School of Law.\u00a0In 1977, he graduated with a Bachelors of Science in Business Administration with an emphasis in Finance &amp; Marketing from Loyola Marymount University,  Fresno. Mr. Murphy is also\u00a0a past-president for the\u00a0Thousand Oaks Rotary Club. \u00a0He has been a dedicated member of the Rotary Club and the Chamber of Commerce for over 30 years.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Finally, Michael was born and raised in  Fresno, CA and is a fourth-generation Californian. He is also an avid Dodgers, Lakers, and L.A. Rams fan. During his time off, he enjoys spending weekends in La Jolla and in Mammoth Lakes with his wife, kids, and grandkids.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><\/h3>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Education<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Southwestern University School of Law, Juris Doctor<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Loyola Marymount University, Bachelors of Science in Business 